Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I have obtained a disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Just one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We can bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I just know that\Nthe discs will bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's call it{\i}\N{\i1}Operation Savage Garden for now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You should take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,He can aid your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,His name is Weather Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' Jack Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But where did he go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get the disc back!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EPISODE 11: OPERATION Savage Garden\N(HEAD TO THE COURTYARD!) (2)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Emergency alarm activated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Corridor 7B.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}-Yes, that's correct. Corridor 7B.\N-{\i1}Emergency alarm activated{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,We are awaiting reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We aren't sure as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:37.82,Main,,0,0,0,,But Corridor 7B's sole function\Nis for access to the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no possibility\Nthat it is a fire or a prisoner riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I trust this prison and the prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,With all the commotion,\Ncuriosity got the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Surely, you are aware
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,that no prisoner has managed\Nto escape from this prison for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the courtyard\Nis outside of Corridor 7B.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No prisoner would choose\Nto escape from there, of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You're quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing out of curiosity…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Is the clock on the wall accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It is now 11:58 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}11:51 a.m.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1} A call to The Speedwagon Foundation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I have the usual request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like access to the collect call list\Nand the recorded conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Women's prison, phone booth 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,The call from about seven minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you touched me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,you are now weightless too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see our enemy anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to retrieve the disc right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,He must be within this laundry room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.59,Main,,0,0,0,,He is lurking somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The courtyard is past that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You are trying to reach that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.35,Main,,0,0,0,,but it is most likely locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.77,Main,,0,0,0,,You might need to blast it,\Nor force it open somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.06,Main,,0,0,0,,There's... A slight problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I know now's not the time for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a personal thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's urgent, and I need to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So, like…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why it suddenly so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's something that happens to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,it's the P-word related to\Nthe pelvic area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad it's not "number two."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, the biological phenomenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You need to take a piss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,No need to say it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm serious. I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Just pick any corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit, why did I even try\Ntalking to a guy about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I have relieved myself already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,See? It's floating over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In zero gravity, the blood in your body{\i}\N{\i1}will suddenly collect in your head.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blood that is usually in the lower parts{\i}\N{\i1}of the body due to gravity.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The space between the skin and the bone{\i}\N{\i1}is swollen and squishy with blood.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It's called a "moon face."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:53.35,Main,,0,0,0,,it's dangerous when too much blood\Ngoes to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:57.73,Main,,0,0,0,,The kidney automatically works harder\Nto reduce the amount of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,This triggers an acute diuretic effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It attempts to thin the blood content
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,by expelling salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,-But--\N-Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll use my clouds to absorb your urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, what are these droplets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They're leaking out of your cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's being sucked out\Nthrough the gap in the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Blood from the wound I got earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,My nose won't stop bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm having difficulty breathing…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.24,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything I touch becomes zero gravity.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I touched the walls leading to the door.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That means the whole room{\i}\N{\i1}is unaffected by gravity!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,The air!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Air can't stay in zero gravity!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll get pulled by{\i}\N{\i1}the surrounding gravity, and it'll escape!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to close up the gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'll suffocate to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Suffocation isn't our primary concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The blood in our bodies will boil first,\Nleading to our death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:41.58,Main,,0,0,0,,In a vacuum, blood boils up like water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,In a zero-gravity vacuum,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,people's blood will dry up in 20 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,before even suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll reload my bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll get shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We must hide somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.65,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm bleeding out of my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to stop the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Just take shallow breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I gathered what little air\Nis remaining in this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,and covered our bodies with clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Cloud suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,The room is almost a complete vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,This is all the remaining air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Your nosebleed has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:12.55,Main,,0,0,0,,How long can we keep breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I didn't have to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd say about two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a cloud suit on the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,If we don't defeat our enemy\Nwithin that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll be thrown into the vacuum, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.94,Main,,0,0,0,,We must find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether we act or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,his attack will finish us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, now that my nosebleed has stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I notice something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I said two minutes, but it could be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We must find him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Carbon dioxide is increasing as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The laundry hampers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,They aren't floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The hampers over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I touched the walls, shutters,\Nand floor of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why the whole room\Nentered zero gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,and everything is floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But why are those hampers\Nand barrels not floating,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,and attached to the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Also, that enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:20.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is he breathing in a vacuum?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shouldn't his blood be boiling over?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,that's the range of his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,There is a distance range\Nto this zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not the entire room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,An attack range!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.93,Main,,0,0,0,,From here to the hampers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,is about 20 meters or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Zero gravity ends there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,If we can get there,\Nthere will surely be normal air!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You must go, Weather Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,He is outside of the vacuum range.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If you do not control the air now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,we will never reach our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You may be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Outside that hamper…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go, Weather Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The pressure in the suit\Nis becoming strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go before this cloud suit\Ndisperses into the vacuum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can\Nget out of my attack range!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,He's gonna shoot him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll protect Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}STAND NAME: Weather Report\NSTAND MASTER: Weather Report
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.29,Main,,0,0,0,,He's coming around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll charge ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,He's going to reach air in a few meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Once Weather Report gets air,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:39.96,Main,,0,0,0,,he's going to corner you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want air that bad, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No need to even reach the hampers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I just now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,completed my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to ricochet\Nthe bullets to injure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I shot the barrel itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.11,Main,,0,0,0,,A bit of air is left in the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Highly pressurized air
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,on the verge of explosion, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,He was pushed back to zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,He is done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,He won't be able to gain enough force\Nto stop the momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The suit itself is about to collapse!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne! How reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You must go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,He'll shoot you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That thrust itself\Nwill dissipate your suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,She makes incredibly quick decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She charged into that bastard\Nto stop his movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,and to push him outside of\Nthe zero gravity again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.26,Main,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Stand is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:28.57,Main,,0,0,0,,My rotating bullets aren't fast enough,\Nand would get flicked away in defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I've been preparing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I've looked for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd captured them away from view.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,There were quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rats! They're alive!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could they be…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Push them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I did not expect you to fight\Nagainst my ability like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,This is checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You're finished, Kujo Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.90,Main,,0,0,0,,My mission is now complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' Jack Flash is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was imprisoned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,With this ability I obtained here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,there is nothing I can't do in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,My future is rosy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I will hand this disc over to Whitesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I can defeat him too, if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,WIth my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I was waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for you to reload.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was waiting with my threads ready{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for you to reload your gun.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.55,Main,,0,0,0,,And you shot at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,These threads!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,When the hell did you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You are the one in a complete vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,without a suit, your blood will boil up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,and explode faster than us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,you must deactivate\Nthe zero gravity immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The crime that put me in this prison…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many times did I stab her?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I killed the female professor,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the prosecutor said{\i}\N{\i1}I stabbed her 69 times.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That compulsion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's surging within me once more.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let you underestimate me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bitch!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.37,Main,,0,0,0,,A reaction between hydrogen peroxide\Nand manganese dioxide
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,produces oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Just like the oxygen in this bottle,\Nit keeps coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,My urge to slaughter someone\Nlike back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:39.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make a headstone out of\Nyour piss-soaked body with this glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jolyne,\Nyour blood vessels will rupture first
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,since you are covered in wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I got incarcerated for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I will kill you\Nand leave this place an invincible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,This will be sufficient
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,just to take the disc back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,from that bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.52,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:36.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! My body is at its limit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I deactivate my ability,{\i}\N{\i1}the air will rush in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may be able to escape using the impact!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Zero gravity, deactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Jumpin' Jack Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You should've deactivated it\Nthe first chance you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The change in air pressure\Nmight have let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If only you had deactivated it while\Nyou still had distance from Stone Free.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The air is blowing you back toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,How much longer\Nuntil The Speedwagon Foundation arrives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Three minutes? Or two minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a corridor past this door.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alongside the right wall, there are{\i}\N{\i1}windows that look out to the courtyard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There, you'll be able to see{\i}\N{\i1}a revolving door's gate.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This gate leads to the courtyard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gate is accessible{\i}\N{\i1}during the day and is unlocked.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The next challenge\Nis how to go about opening this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get a prison guard to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We have his work permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.42,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll trick them into opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Once the door opens,\Nyou'll knock the guards out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,and force your way to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Not only will you be charged\Nwith attempted escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,but you'll also receive\Nsolitary confinement for six months
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,where you cannot even\Nexercise sufficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the courtyard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.49,Main,,0,0,0,,and hand this disc over to someone\Nfrom The Speedwagon Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:51.58,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my only mission in life right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,The guards are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Weather Report,\Ngo find somewhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go by myself from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You're severely wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,and if the guards see your injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,they might lock the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Very well. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you knocking?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,"It's you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it, Rangler?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this noise about?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold still. I'll open the door.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.51,Main,,0,0,0,,If you are returning to the men's prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Lang Rangler, how about we stop\Nby the chapel on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a guard!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is he?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:10.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's neither a guard nor a prisoner!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What could his attire mean?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Subtitle translation by: Megumi Hunter
